## Versioning (High-Level)

- Prefer **URL-based versions** (`/api/v1/...`, `/api/v2/...`) or header-based versioning
- Keep old versions stable while evolving new ones

These guidelines are framework-agnostic; adapt the routing syntax to your framework, but keep the **RESTful shapes and naming** consistent.
